<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            color: #333; 
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
        }
        .container { 
            max-width: 600px; 
            margin: 0 auto; 
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white; 
            padding: 40px 20px; 
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content { 
            padding: 40px; 
            background: white;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .otp-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f6f8ff 0%, #f0f4ff 100%);
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 2px dashed #c7d2fe;
        }
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 10px;
            color: #4f46e5;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.15);
        }
        .expiry-note {
            background: #fef3c7; 
            padding: 16px; 
            border-left: 4px solid #d97706;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .footer { 
            text-align: center; 
            padding: 30px 20px; 
            color: #6b7280; 
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        p {
            margin: 16px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
        }
        .warning-text {
            color: #92400e;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .instruction-list {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .instruction-list li {
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: #4b5563;
        }
        .support-contact {
            background: #ecfdf5;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #10b981;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container { padding: 10px; }
            .content { padding: 20px; }
            .otp-code { font-size: 36px; padding: 15px 25px; }
            .header { padding: 30px 15px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Your One-Time Password (OTP)</h1>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; opacity: 0.9; font-size: 16px;">
                Secure Verification Code
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div class="logo">YourApp</div>
            </div>
            
            <p>Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
            
            <p>You've requested to verify your identity. Use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to complete your verification:</p>
            
            <div class="otp-container">
                <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">Your verification code:</p>
                <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
                    (Valid for {{validity}} minutes)
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="expiry-note">
                <p style="margin: 0;" class="warning-text">
                    ‚ö†Ô∏è <strong>Important:</strong> 
                    This code will expire in {{validity}} minutes. Do not share this code with anyone.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="instruction-list">
                <p style="margin-top: 0; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">To use this OTP:</p>
                <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin: 10px 0;">
                    <li>Enter the code on the verification page</li>
                    <li>Do not refresh or navigate away from the page</li>
                    <li>Complete verification within {{validity}} minutes</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>Why you received this email:</strong></p>
            <p>This OTP was requested for: <strong>{{purpose}}</strong></p>
            
            <div class="support-contact">
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #065f46; font-size: 14px;">
                    üíÅ <strong>Need help?</strong> If you didn't request this code or need assistance, 
                    please contact our support team immediately.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                <strong>Best regards,</strong><br>
                <span style="color: #6b7280;">The Security Team at YourApp</span>
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p style="margin: 0;">
                &copy; {{year}} YourApp. All rights reserved.<br>
                This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">
                For your security, never share your OTP with anyone.<br>
                YourApp will never ask for your password or OTP via email or phone.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>